1. Ancient Times, Download
 
Ancient Times is on GitHub.
 
https://github.com/jheiska2/Ancient-Times
 
Dowload it and point browser to index.php. That should be enough.
 
An example of a standard installation of ancient times is available here.  
 
http://www.student.bth.se/~jahb08/me/forumRomanum/?m=rom&p=topics 

2. Ancient Times, A template for websites
 
Ancient Times is to be a complete and powerful webbtemplate with a minimum of code. A kind of CMS for developers.
This project is part of a course at Blekinge Technical University where my teacher Mikael Roos made the Persia template
available for download at github, link is up in the left corner to my teachers link.

3. Ancient Times, The name
 
The name is from the topic in our class "Persia" and it sounded nice with a ancient times topic.
It has a history which can connect to this software project.
 
